<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-856] Correlation id for OffsetFetch request (#2) always responds with 0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-856</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The in the new Kafka when making an OffsetFetch request the correlation id always response is always sent as 0. It doesn&apos;t matter if the client request specifies a correlation id other then 0.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example wireshark capture:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;00000000  00 00 00 31 00 07 00 00  00 00 00 2a 00 03 66 6f ...1.... ...*..fo&lt;br/&gt;
00000010  6f 00 0a 74 65 73 74 2d  67 72 6f 75 70 00 00 00 o..test- group...&lt;br/&gt;
00000020  01 00 0a 74 65 73 74 5f  74 6f 70 69 63 00 00 00 ...test_ topic...&lt;br/&gt;
00000030  01 00 00 00 00                                   .....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Request #1&lt;br/&gt;
--------&lt;br/&gt;
len:    00 00 00 31&lt;br/&gt;
api:    00 07&lt;br/&gt;
ver:    00 00&lt;br/&gt;
cor:    00 00 00 2a&lt;br/&gt;
cid:    2a 00 03 66 6f 6f&lt;br/&gt;
....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;00000000  00 00 00 2d 00 00 00 2a  00 03 66 6f 6f 00 00 00 ...-...* ..foo...&lt;br/&gt;
00000010  01 00 0a 74 65 73 74 5f  74 6f 70 69 63 00 00 00 ...test_ topic...&lt;br/&gt;
00000020  01 00 00 00 00 ff ff ff  ff ff ff ff ff 00 00 00 ........ ........&lt;br/&gt;
00000030  03&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Response #1&lt;br/&gt;
--------&lt;br/&gt;
len:    00 00 00 2d&lt;br/&gt;
cor:    00 00 00 2a&lt;br/&gt;
cid:    2a 00 03 66 6f 6f&lt;br/&gt;
....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;00000035  00 00 00 35 00 02 00 00  00 00 00 2a 00 03 66 6f ...5.... ...*..fo&lt;br/&gt;
00000045  6f ff ff ff ff 00 00 00  01 00 0a 74 65 73 74 5f o....... ...test_&lt;br/&gt;
00000055  74 6f 70 69 63 00 00 00  01 00 00 00 00 ff ff ff topic... ........&lt;br/&gt;
00000065  ff ff ff ff fe 00 00 00  01                      ........ .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Request #2&lt;br/&gt;
---------&lt;br/&gt;
len:    00 00 00 35&lt;br/&gt;
api:    00 02&lt;br/&gt;
ver:    00 00&lt;br/&gt;
cor:    00 00 00 2a&lt;br/&gt;
cid:    00 03 66 6f 6f&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;00000031  00 00 00 2a 00 00 00 00  00 00 00 01 00 0a 74 65 ...*.... ......te&lt;br/&gt;
00000041  73 74 5f 74 6f 70 69 63  00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00 st_topic ........&lt;br/&gt;
00000051  00 00 00 00 00 01 00 00  00 00 00 00 00 00       ........ ......&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Response #2:&lt;br/&gt;
----------&lt;br/&gt;
len:    00 00 00 2a&lt;br/&gt;
cor:    00 00 00 00&lt;br/&gt;
alen:   00 00 00 01&lt;br/&gt;
....&lt;/p&gt;</description>
